<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDateOfAmendment" id="idb0930507-2930-11f1-a69d-9cbca84c43f0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date of 2008 Amendment</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Amendment by <ref href="/us/pl/110/181">Pub. L. 110–181</ref> effective as of <date date="2007-12-31">Dec. 31, 2007</date>, and subject to various special provisions, see <ref href="/us/pl/110/181/s610">section 610 of Pub. L. 110–181</ref>, set out as a Correction of Lapsed Authorities for Payment of Bonuses, Special Pays, and Similar Benefits for Members of the Uniformed Services note under <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s2130a">section 2130a of Title 10</ref>, Armed Forces.</p>
